        <h2>Shadertoy Outputs</h2>
        <hr>
        Image shaders: fragColor is used as output channel. It is not, for =
now, mandatory but recommended to leave the alpha channel to 1.0.<br>
        <br>
        Sound shaders: the mainSound() function returns a vec2 containing t=
he left and right (stereo) sound channel wave data.
